						               													<description>North Star Games has been working on a complete redesign of the Evolution system since 2018.  Here are some of the goals:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Make all Expansions Compatible &amp;#10;         Players can add as many (or as few) expansions as they want.&amp;#10;         Easier to setup and breakdown. &amp;#10;         Smaller expansions, but more of them.&amp;#10;    &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Make the base game a more gentle and inviting experience to new players &amp;#10;         Less punitive to players who get targeted.&amp;#10;         Remove the snowballing that happens when a player is targeted or gets off to a poor start. &amp;#10;         Fewer traits, but with more synergies. &amp;#10;    &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first point will fix two issues: 1) Flight and Climate are incompatible, and 2) Changing between expansions is extremely cumbersome and easy to mess up.  With the new system, gamers will be able to create an epic experience by picking and choosing a mix of their favorite expansions. It will also allow casual gamers to step up slowly by learning 1 small expansion at a time.  Smaller expansions also mean we can release 1 or 2 of them each year.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The second point will create a better experience to players who are new to the game system, including heavy gamers, casual gamers, and families using Nature as educational entertainment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The final polish was given to Nature early in 2022.  We are now testing expansions. Here's a link if you want to try the game before it gets released. Playing the game is the first step towards become a playtester: https://forms.gle/DPndQZRaV9RgXV4M8.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Theme &amp;amp; Gameplay&amp;#10;Players adapt their species in a dynamic ecosystem where food is scarce, predators lurk, and symbiotic relationships abound. Traits like Claws and Horns will protect your species from Predators, while being Opportunist can open up creative ways to find food.  Gather your friends and see who best adapts to the changing world around them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
